{
  "text": "Plasma corticosterone levels were measured using a commercial kit (Corticosterone ELISA kit; Enzo Life Sciences, Farmingdale, NY) as per the manufacturer's instructions, and the concentration of each sample was extrapolated from a standard curve. Sensitivity of the assay is \u03fd27.0 pg/ml. This was carried out pre-and postacute water stress using the forced swim test [CITATION_1] .",
  "correct_citation": {
    "[CITATION_1]": "37542703"
